@startuml
title Processos principais - US 2.2.3 Manage Docks

start
:Port Officer opens Dock management UI (or uses API);
:Sends POST /api/Docks with CreateDockDTO;
if (valid data?) then (yes)
  :API validates and maps DTO -> Dock model;
  :API queries VesselType ids and populates relations;
  :API saves Dock to DB;
  :API returns 201 Created with DockDTO;
else (no)
  :API returns 400 Bad Request with validation errors;
endif
stop

@enduml
